Aoskar, also known as the Power of Portals and the Keeper of Gateways, was venerated as the god of portals within his own temple in the City of Doors. After a failed attempt to wrest control of Sigil from the Lady of Pain, the Lady slew Aoskar and cast out his corpse into the Astral Plane.

Domains: Arcana
Alignment: Neutral
